## Daily Analytics Reporting — Detail

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron
    participant GA as Google Analytics
    participant AI as GPT-3.5-turbo
    participant Email as SMTP
    
    Cron->>GA: Query: Sessions, Users by Date (Last 24h)
    GA-->>Cron: JSON Metrics
    Cron->>AI: "Summarize this GA report: {metrics}"
    AI-->>Cron: 3-Bullet Executive Summary
    Cron->>Email: Send to team@company.com
    Email-->>Team: "Daily Website Performance Summary"
```

### GA Query Configuration
```json
{
  "viewId": "UA-XXXXXX-Y",
  "metrics": ["ga:sessions", "ga:users", "ga:pageviews", "ga:bounceRate"],
  "dimensions": ["ga:date", "ga:sourceMedium", "ga:deviceCategory"],
  "dateRange": "yesterday"
}
```

### AI Prompt Template
```
Summarize this Google Analytics report for a non-technical executive audience. 
Focus on: 
1. Key metric changes vs. previous period
2. Top traffic sources 
3. Anomalies or notable patterns
4. One actionable recommendation
Output: 3 bullet points max.
```

