## Feature Engineering Advisor — Detail

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant HTTP as HTTP Request
    participant Code as Code Node (Analysis)
    participant LLM as GPT-4.1-mini
    participant HTML as HTML Output
    
    User->>HTTP: Trigger with CSV URL
    HTTP-->>Code: Raw CSV Data
    Code->>Code: Parse CSV, detect column types, compute stats
    Code-->>LLM: Dataset Summary + Column Analysis
    LLM->>LLM: Generate Feature Engineering Strategy
    LLM-->>HTML: Styled Recommendations
    HTML-->>User: Visual Report
```

### Code Node Analysis Output
```json
{
  "dataset_summary": {
    "total_rows": 1000,
    "total_columns": 10,
    "missing_percentage": 5.2
  },
  "feature_engineering_context": {
    "numeric_columns": ["height", "weight", "age"],
    "categorical_columns": ["gender", "city", "occupation"],
    "high_cardinality_categorical": ["city", "occupation"],
    "datetime_columns": ["created_at"],
    "target_candidates": ["income", "churn"]
  },
  "data_quality": {
    "total_missing_values": 520,
    "columns_with_missing": ["occupation", "income"],
    "duplicate_rows": 3
  }
}
```

### LLM Prompt Focus Areas
| Category | Focus |
|----------|-------|
| **Business Logic** | Why each feature adds value |
| **Data Relationships** | Cross-column combinations, ratios, interactions |
| **Domain Insights** | Context-specific patterns (healthcare, finance, retail) |
| **Modeling Impact** | Predictive power, leakage prevention, interpretability |
| **Implementation** | SQL/Python/pandas agnostic concepts |

