## Extending the Analytics Stack

| Need | Current | Extension Path |
|------|---------|----------------|
| **Real-time Dashboards** | Daily email | Add Superset / Grafana → Query GA/Postgres |
| **Anomaly Detection** | Manual review | Add statistical anomaly detection in Code Node |
| **Multi-Source** | GA only | Add Search Console, Ads, CRM data |
| **Team Customization** | Single email | Per-role summaries (exec vs. marketing vs. dev) |
| **Historical Trends** | Daily snapshot | Store in Postgres → Trend analysis workflow |
| **Cost Attribution** | Not tracked | Join with ad spend data → ROAS calculation |